import React from 'react' import { ProjectsContainer, ImgContainer, Img, SummaryContainer, Summary, SkillsContainer, SkillsUsed, SkillsList, Skill, ProjectLinkContainer, ProjectLink, Header, HeaderContainer, VideoContainer, VideoHeader } from './ProjectElements' const ProjectSection = ({ id, header, img, imgHeight, videoHeader, videoURL, imgWidth, summary, skills, projectLinkDesc, projectLinkUrl }) => { return ( <>
{header}
 {videoHeader} Summary: {summary} Skills Used: {skills.map((skillValue, index) => { return ({skillValue}) })} {projectLinkDesc} ) } export default ProjectSection
